text: Pieter van Dam (21 May 1904 - 11 February 1985) was a Dutch gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1904 births Category:1985 deaths Category:Dutch male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the Netherlands Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from The Hague
